OL,3,CBereaved mothers call for independent
OL,4,Cgoverning body for Scouts
OL,6,FThe mothers of two boys who died two
OL,7,Fdecades apart have called for an
OL,8,Findependent body to govern the Scouts
OL,9,FAssociation. North of England
OL,10,Fcorrespondent Kelly Foran sat down
OL,11,Fwith them.
OL,13,FTwo mothers of Scouts who have joined
OL,14,Fforces to call for a public enquiry
OL,15,Finto The Scout Association.
OL,17,FJackie Leonard and Sharon Collins want
OL,18,Fthe organisation to be externally
OL,19,Fgoverned after their young children
OL,20,Fdied 20 years apart, in almost
OL,21,Fidentical circumstances.
