OL,3,CBereaved mothers call for independent
OL,4,Cgoverning body for Scouts
OL,6,FScott and Ben are among 11 Scouts who
OL,7,Fwent on camping trips and never came
OL,8,Fhome.
OL,10,FTheir mums are now connected through
OL,11,Ftheir grief, and their campaign for
OL,12,Ffundamental changes to the way the
OL,13,Forganisation is governed.
OL,15,FBen Leonard, 16, from Stockport,
OL,16,FGreater Manchester, had just purchased
OL,17,Fa copy of Pride and Prejudice from a
OL,18,Fcharity shop in Llandudno when he went
OL,19,Fon a hike with his Scout group.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/9
