OL,6,FHe was on a trip with Reddish Explorer
OL,7,FScouts in August 2018 when he suffered
OL,8,Fa serious head injury after falling
OL,9,Ffrom a cliff on the Great Orme in
OL,10,FNorth Wales.
OL,12,FFollowing a two-month inquest at
OL,13,FManchester Civil Courts of Justice, a
OL,14,Fjury found Ben was unlawfully killed
OL,15,Fby the most senior Scout leader on the
OL,16,Ftrip and an assistant Scout leader.
OL,18,FThe jury also found that this was
OL,19,Fcontributed to by neglect by The Scout
OL,20,FAssociation.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/9
