OL,4,Cgoverning body for Scouts
OL,6,FJackie said: "This is why they need to
OL,7,Fhave a regulatory model like Ofsted,
OL,8,Flike the schools, to oversee outdoor
OL,9,Factivities.
OL,11,F"If you're taking children on outdoor
OL,12,Factivities and things like that they
OL,13,Fneed to be properly audited and
OL,14,Fregulated.
OL,16,F"There's over half a million young
OL,17,Fpeople and children that they're
OL,18,Flooking after and come under the
OL,19,FScouts.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/9
