OL,6,FHis mother Sharon contacted Jackie
OL,7,Fwhen she saw on the news what happened
OL,8,Fto her son.
OL,10,F"They need to use what happened to the
OL,11,Fboys previously as as examples of
OL,12,Flearning. And that should form part of
OL,13,Fthe training. And don't just forget
OL,14,Fabout them as if their lives didn't
OL,15,Fmatter, because the lives did matter."
