OL,4,Cgoverning body for Scouts
OL,6,FJennie Price, chairwoman of The Scout
OL,7,FAssociation Board of Trustees, said:
OL,8,F"We take today's conclusion extremely
OL,9,Fseriously. We want to restate our
OL,10,Fwholehearted apology to Ben Leonard's
OL,11,Ffamily and our deepest sympathies
OL,12,Fcontinue to be with his family and
OL,13,Ffriends.
