OL,3,CBereaved mothers call for independent
OL,4,Cgoverning body for Scouts
OL,6,F"As an organisation we are committed
OL,7,Fto learning. The jury heard how in
OL,8,Fthis instance the local leaders did
OL,9,Fnot follow our safety rules and
OL,10,Fprocesses. As a result of Ben's tragic
OL,11,Fdeath in 2018, we have already made
OL,12,Fmany changes to our risk assessments,
OL,13,Fsafety rules, training and support we
OL,14,Fgive our volunteers."
OL,16,FShe added: "Keeping young people safe
OL,17,Ffrom harm remains our number one
OL,18,Fpriority at scouts. We emphatically
OL,19,Frefute allegations made in court about
OL,20,Fany criminal action on behalf of The
OL,21,FScout Association."
